<p>https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/study-found-plastic-in-every-seafood-sample-it-analyzed </p>
<p>https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.est.0c02337 </p>
<p>https://pubs.acs.org/doi/pdf/10.1021/acs.est.0c02337 </p>
